WEBVTT

00:00.991 --> 00:03.637
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

00:03.637 --> 00:05.739
I SAW THE PREGNANCY TEST
IN THE BATHROOM.

00:05.739 --> 00:06.873
I KNOW WHAT'S COMING

00:06.873 --> 00:09.009
AND I'M WILLING TO PAY
FOR THE PROCEDURE.

00:09.009 --> 00:10.511
WHEN I GOT IN THE SAME CAR,

00:10.511 --> 00:13.379
I GOT PULLED OVER AND SAW
THE OTHER $50,000 IN A BAG.

00:13.379 --> 00:15.148
IT WAS TAN,
LIKE A MAN'S BAG.

00:15.148 --> 00:16.883
HAD LEATHER STRAPS ON IT.

00:16.883 --> 00:19.219
NOW, JIM WAS HAVING AN AFFAIR
WITH CANDACE YOUNG.

00:19.219 --> 00:21.888
SHE WAS BLACKMAILING HIM
FOR $100,000 AND A CAR.

00:21.888 --> 00:26.092
YOU DELIVERED THAT CAR
WITH TWO KILOS OF COCAINE IN IT.

00:26.092 --> 00:27.894
WHO TOLD YOU?

00:27.894 --> 00:30.697
YOU JUST DID.

00:30.697 --> 00:32.398
WELL?

00:34.935 --> 00:36.603
YES, I LIED.

00:36.603 --> 00:38.839
WELL, I KNOW THAT.

00:38.839 --> 00:40.941
I'M SORRY.

00:42.408 --> 00:43.409
BABY.

00:43.409 --> 00:46.379
MNH‐MNH. NO. DON'T.

00:46.379 --> 00:49.215
I AM SORRY.

00:49.215 --> 00:53.554
I WANT HIM
OUT OF JAIL <i>TODAY.</i>

00:53.554 --> 00:55.522
TODAY
MAY NOT BE POSSIBLE.

00:55.522 --> 00:56.790
MAKE IT HAPPEN.

00:56.790 --> 00:57.858
I'LL TRY.

00:57.858 --> 00:59.092
MNH‐MNH.

00:59.092 --> 01:00.934
YOU DON'T TRY.

01:00.934 --> 01:02.803
YOU DO IT.

01:03.904 --> 01:06.540
NOW, YOU KNOW THAT
THIS MAY TAKE SOME TIME.

01:06.540 --> 01:08.374
I DON'T CARE.

01:08.374 --> 01:10.210
LOOK,
I'VE ALREADY ARRANGED

01:10.210 --> 01:12.613
FOR A FEW THINGS
TO GET TAKEN CARE OF.

01:12.613 --> 01:14.615
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR
ABOUT ANY OF THAT.

01:14.615 --> 01:15.716
I DON'T CARE.

01:15.716 --> 01:18.585
I WANT HIM
OUT OF JAIL TODAY.

01:19.720 --> 01:22.088
OKAY.

01:22.088 --> 01:24.490
OKAY.

01:26.426 --> 01:28.161
THANK YOU.

01:36.703 --> 01:38.238
YOU CARE TO KNOW WHY?

01:38.238 --> 01:40.340
YOU WANT TO TALK
ABOUT THIS?

01:41.474 --> 01:43.544
TALK ABOUT WHAT?

01:45.311 --> 01:48.849
TALK ABOUT THE FACT
THAT THE MAN THAT I LOVE...

01:48.849 --> 01:51.952
THE MAN THAT I HAVE
A CHILD WITH...

01:51.952 --> 01:55.956
HAVE BEEN THROUGH
SO MANY UPS AND DOWNS WITH...

01:55.956 --> 01:59.726
THE MAN THAT'S
BEEN BY MY SIDE...

01:59.726 --> 02:01.835
FOR 25 YEARS...

02:01.835 --> 02:05.405
IS A GRACEFUL LIAR.

02:06.472 --> 02:07.741
SWEETHEART.

02:07.741 --> 02:09.643
Shh.

02:09.643 --> 02:12.846
I WOULD HAVE
RATHER COME HOME...

02:12.846 --> 02:15.281
TO FIND YOU IN BED
WITH ANOTHER WOMAN.

02:16.382 --> 02:18.284
AN AFFAIR.

02:18.284 --> 02:21.121
AN AFFAIR...

02:21.121 --> 02:23.156
I COULD TOUCH,
I COULD FEEL.

02:23.156 --> 02:24.891
IT'S TANGIBLE.

02:24.891 --> 02:28.695
BUT A LIE,
IT'S INVISIBLE.

02:28.695 --> 02:30.897
IT'S DEADLY.

02:30.897 --> 02:33.333
IT KILLS HOPE AND TRUST.

02:33.333 --> 02:35.536
AND THE FACT THAT A LIE

02:35.536 --> 02:40.440
CAN ROLL OFF OF YOUR LIPS
SO EASILY, SO GRACEFULLY,

02:40.440 --> 02:43.243
MAKES ME WONDER IF ANYTHING
YOU EVER SAID TO ME

02:43.243 --> 02:44.745
WAS TRUE.

02:46.913 --> 02:50.383
DAVID, I ASKED YOU
A DIRECT QUESTION.

02:51.885 --> 02:54.988
AND YOU LOOKED AT ME...

02:54.988 --> 02:57.691
AND YOU LIED...

02:57.691 --> 02:59.459
GRACEFULLY.

03:02.168 --> 03:06.406
I CAN FORGIVE
A LOT OF THINGS...

03:06.406 --> 03:09.676
BUT A LIE,
I CANNOT SUFFER.

03:11.678 --> 03:14.147
A LIE CAN ROLL OFF
OF YOUR LIPS

03:14.147 --> 03:16.482
AS EASILY
AS "I LOVE YOU" CAN.

03:18.685 --> 03:21.622
AND I WILL FOREVER WONDER

03:21.622 --> 03:26.292
IF WHAT YOU'RE SAYING TO ME
IS THE TRUTH...

03:26.292 --> 03:28.294
OR IS IT A LIE?

03:33.199 --> 03:35.536
BABY...

03:35.536 --> 03:37.971
I DO LOVE YOU.

03:39.773 --> 03:42.709
AND I AM TRULY SORRY.

03:42.709 --> 03:44.377
[ SIGHS ]

03:45.912 --> 03:48.381
THAT WAS GRACEFUL.

03:48.381 --> 03:49.983
[ SIGHS ]

03:49.983 --> 03:51.852
BUT IS IT A LIE?

