YEAH.

29:56.723 --> 29:57.858
WHAT HAPPENED?

29:57.858 --> 29:59.860
I DON'T KNOW. I GUESS
THE D. A. LOST THE EVIDENCE

29:59.860 --> 30:00.801
OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

30:00.801 --> 30:01.968
THEY LOST IT?

30:01.968 --> 30:03.336
Yeah.

30:03.336 --> 30:05.839
WOW. OKAY.

30:05.839 --> 30:09.810
WELL, BENNY, THANK YOU
FOR CALLING ME TO TELL ME.

30:09.810 --> 30:11.978
I'M SORRY.
I WOULD HAVE CALLED YOU SOONER,

30:11.978 --> 30:14.648
BUT, YOU KNOW, MAMA WON'T
LET ME OUT OF HER SIGHT NOW.

30:14.648 --> 30:16.349
I UNDERSTAND.

30:16.349 --> 30:18.151
WELL, LOOK, MAMA'S GONNA BE
LOOKING FOR ME ANY MINUTE,

30:18.151 --> 30:19.553
ALL RIGHT,
SO I'LL GIVE YOU A CALL LATER.

30:19.553 --> 30:21.421
ALL RIGHT, LOVE YOU.

30:21.421 --> 30:23.156
I LOVE YOU MORE, B.

30:23.156 --> 30:24.257
Okay, bye.

30:24.257 --> 30:26.560
BYE.

30:39.139 --> 30:42.375
HEY.
YOU MISSED DINNER.

30:43.644 --> 30:44.878
I'M NOT HUNGRY.

30:44.878 --> 30:48.882
WELL, I‐I LEFT IT
IN THE OVEN FOR YOU.

30:48.882 --> 30:51.284
WHY?

30:51.284 --> 30:54.521
[ CHUCKLES ]
BECAUSE YOU NEED TO EAT.

30:54.521 --> 30:57.724
WHAT I NEED IS TO GET
OUT OF HERE, JEFFREY.

31:00.093 --> 31:02.268
WELL, SOON ENOUGH.

31:02.268 --> 31:04.638
I MEAN,
YOU'RE DOING A LOT BETTER.

31:04.638 --> 31:07.373
