31:54.120 --> 31:57.924
YES, I DID, WYATT.

31:57.924 --> 32:01.101
SO YOU LIED TO ME?

32:01.101 --> 32:02.836
YES.

32:05.706 --> 32:08.709
I'M SORRY.
I WAS TRYING TO PROTECT YOU.

32:08.709 --> 32:11.578
DON'T YOU KNOW HOW MUCH
I WANT YOU TO MAKE IT?

32:11.578 --> 32:13.814
WHY?

32:15.348 --> 32:17.918
YOU'RE MY CLOSEST FRIEND,
WYATT.

32:17.918 --> 32:20.787
YOUR CLOSEST...FRIEND?

32:20.787 --> 32:23.056
YES.

32:24.758 --> 32:26.359
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THE HARDEST PART

32:26.359 --> 32:27.828
ABOUT BEING HERE IS,
JEFFREY?

32:27.828 --> 32:29.730
WHAT'S THAT?

32:29.730 --> 32:31.898
THE LONELINESS.

32:34.167 --> 32:36.402
WELL, YOU HAVE ME.

32:36.402 --> 32:37.971
DO I?

32:37.971 --> 32:40.574
YEAH, WYATT.

32:40.574 --> 32:42.843
DO YOU EVER GET LONELY?

32:45.145 --> 32:47.514
