32:47.514 --> 32:49.783
DO YOU EVER
WANT TO SLEEP WITH ME?

32:54.054 --> 32:55.288
WHAT?

32:55.288 --> 32:58.024
W‐WHY ARE YOU
SAYING THAT TO ME, WYATT?

32:58.024 --> 33:00.300
BECAUSE
I WAS HOPING YOU DID.

33:02.869 --> 33:04.671
UH...

33:04.671 --> 33:07.340
WYATT, I, UM...

33:09.109 --> 33:12.045
I DON'T ‐‐
I DON'T ‐‐ I DON'T...

33:12.045 --> 33:13.313
I DON'T ‐‐ I...

33:18.151 --> 33:19.720
DO YOU WANT TO KNOW
THE TRUTH?

33:21.487 --> 33:22.488
HMM?

33:22.488 --> 33:23.557
WHOA.

33:23.557 --> 33:24.958
SORRY. YEAH.

33:24.958 --> 33:27.227
I‐I‐I DO.

33:30.664 --> 33:31.732
JEFFREY...

33:33.567 --> 33:35.869
...I'M IN LOVE WITH YOU.

33:35.869 --> 33:38.905
I DON'T KNOW HOW
TO SAY IT.

33:42.175 --> 33:43.610
AH.

33:43.610 --> 33:45.378
WYATT, UM...

33:47.247 --> 33:48.248
[ SIGHS ]

33:48.248 --> 33:51.017
I WAS HOPING
THAT YOU FELT THE SAME WAY.

33:55.221 --> 33:59.025
I‐I‐I'M SORRY,
I‐I‐I DON'T.

34:00.226 --> 34:01.935
REALLY?

34:04.738 --> 34:07.040
HMM?

34:07.040 --> 34:09.610
IT'S OKAY.

34:09.610 --> 34:11.878
JEFFREY, YOU CAN TELL ME.

34:14.581 --> 34:17.150
JEFFREY?

34:17.150 --> 34:18.852
[ STUTTERS ]

34:18.852 --> 34:21.454
YOU'LL FIND YOUR WAY.

34:29.062 --> 34:30.764
WHY ARE YOU STILL
TOUCHING MY LEG?

34:31.865 --> 34:33.934
I KNOW.

34:33.934 --> 34:36.002
W‐WYATT, I...

34:36.002 --> 34:38.371
