UNCOMFORTABLE?

34:39.806 --> 34:41.074
HMM?

34:41.074 --> 34:42.909
NO, BUT THIS IS
INAPPROPRIATE.

34:42.909 --> 34:44.277
I‐I ‐‐
WHOA, NO, NO.

34:44.277 --> 34:46.246
A KISS WOULD BE
INAPPROPRIATE.

34:47.748 --> 34:49.015
KISS ME.

34:49.015 --> 34:50.483
[ SIGHS ]

34:50.483 --> 34:52.252
WYATT, I'M NOT GAY.

34:52.252 --> 34:54.755
WHAT'S THAT BULGE?

34:54.755 --> 34:57.157
IT'S OKAY.

34:57.157 --> 34:58.559
I'VE BEEN WATCHING YOU.

34:58.559 --> 35:00.967
I KNOW YOU WANT ME, JEFFREY.
IT'S OKAY.

35:02.035 --> 35:03.336
I DON'T. I DON'T.

35:03.336 --> 35:04.337
YES, YOU DO.

35:04.337 --> 35:06.640
I KNOW YOU DO.

35:08.008 --> 35:11.211
PLEASE...
TAKE YOUR HAND OFF ME.

35:11.211 --> 35:12.445
NO.

35:13.479 --> 35:15.281
NO.
WYATT...

35:15.281 --> 35:17.884
WHY DON'T YOU
JUST TELL ME, OKAY?

35:17.884 --> 35:20.687
JUST TELL ME
THAT YOU WANT ME,

35:20.687 --> 35:22.455
AND WE CAN HAVE
EACH OTHER.

35:22.455 --> 35:24.725
JUST TELL ME
THAT YOU'RE GAY.

35:27.060 --> 35:29.530
I CAN'T. I CAN'T.
I CAN'T.

35:29.530 --> 35:31.832
YES, YOU CAN.

35:33.700 --> 35:35.368
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

35:35.368 --> 35:36.970
HEY, HEY.

35:36.970 --> 35:39.439
HELP ME UNDERSTAND,
OKAY?

35:40.707 --> 35:44.410
HELP ME...UNDERSTAND.

35:46.246 --> 35:48.649
MY ‐‐ MY PARENTS...

35:48.649 --> 35:50.416
THEY'RE NOT HERE.

35:50.416 --> 35:52.519
[ SIGHS ]

35:52.519 --> 35:54.054
MY MOM ‐‐
HEY.

35:54.054 --> 35:57.057
SHE'S NOT HERE, EITHER.

35:57.057 --> 35:59.793
JEFFREY, LOOK AT ME.

36:01.034 --> 36:02.368
JEFFREY, LOOK AT ME.

36:02.368 --> 36:05.038
JUST TELL <i>ME.</i>

36:07.774 --> 36:10.343
YES.

36:10.343 --> 36:12.245
I'M GAY.

36:12.245 --> 36:15.616
IT'S OKAY. RELAX.
IT'S OKAY.

36:18.251 --> 36:20.186
ARE YOU IN LOVE
WITH ME?

36:20.186 --> 36:21.588
[ BREATHES UNEVENLY ]

36:21.588 --> 36:23.289
YES.

36:26.960 --> 36:28.595
I‐I DON'T KNOW
WHEN IT HAPPENED.

36:28.595 --> 36:30.296
I...

36:30.296 --> 36:32.065
I SAW YOU ONE DAY,

36:32.065 --> 36:34.868
AND I JUST LOOKED AT YOU
DIFFERENTLY.

36:34.868 --> 36:36.637
EVERYTHING ‐‐
EVERYTHING CHANGED.

36:36.637 --> 36:39.072
EVERYTHING...

36:39.072 --> 36:41.274
EVERY TIME I'M AROUND YOU
I GET BUTTERFLIES.

36:41.274 --> 36:43.243
MM.

36:43.243 --> 36:45.178
I JUST ‐‐ I JUST...

36:46.913 --> 36:48.882
LIKE NOW?

36:48.882 --> 36:51.151
YES.

36:51.151 --> 36:54.054
SEE, WAS THAT SO HARD?

36:54.054 --> 36:56.489
[ CHUCKLES ]

36:56.489 --> 36:58.592
[ SIGHS ]

36:58.592 --> 37:00.126
NO.

37:00.126 --> 37:02.168
[ SNIFFLES ]

37:02.168 --> 37:03.537
[ SIGHS ]

37:03.537 --> 37:05.004
I FEEL BETTER.

37:05.004 --> 37:08.942
I FEEL ‐‐
I FEEL AFRAID, BUT BETTER.

37:08.942 --> 37:10.977
WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?

37:10.977 --> 37:12.478
THIS IS INAPPROPRIATE.

37:12.478 --> 37:15.014
I'M ‐‐
I'M TRYING TO HELP <i>YOU.</i>

37:15.014 --> 37:16.783
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

37:17.984 --> 37:20.353
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

37:21.755 --> 37:23.590
I'M SO GLAD YOU SAID THAT.

37:23.590 --> 37:26.159
I MEAN,
I‐I THOUGHT THAT YOU WERE.

37:26.159 --> 37:28.995
I MEAN, I FELT
THAT YOU WANTED ME, TOO.

37:28.995 --> 37:31.431
YOU THOUGHT WHAT?

37:33.066 --> 37:34.968
THAT YOU'RE GAY.

37:34.968 --> 37:37.270
I'M NOT.

37:40.541 --> 37:42.375
YOU'RE ‐‐ YOU'RE NOT?

37:42.375 --> 37:44.344
NO.

37:44.344 --> 37:47.313
ARE YOU...BISEXUAL?

37:47.313 --> 37:48.782
NO.

37:48.782 --> 37:52.218
I'M ONLY ATTRACTED
TO WOMEN.

37:52.218 --> 37:54.555
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS
TO ME?

37:54.555 --> 37:57.457
I WANTED TO SEE HOW FAR
YOU'D TAKE THIS, JEFFREY.

37:57.457 --> 38:00.561
I WANTED TO SEE
HOW GULLIBLE YOU ARE,

38:00.561 --> 38:03.837
HOW NAIVE YOU ARE.

38:03.837 --> 38:05.972
I'VE BEEN WATCHING YOU
LICKING YOUR LIPS,

38:05.972 --> 38:07.440
THINKING I WAS ASLEEP,

38:07.440 --> 38:09.676
HOPPING IN THE SAME BED
WITH ME.

38:10.944 --> 38:14.080
JEFFREY, YOU WENT TO HER
AND YOU LIED TO HER.

38:14.080 --> 38:16.850
THEN YOU CAME TO ME
AND YOU LIED TO <i>ME.</i>

38:16.850 --> 38:19.252
JEFFREY,
YOU ARE PATHETIC.

38:19.252 --> 38:22.255
NOBODY HAS EVER DONE ANYTHING
LIKE THIS TO ME.

38:22.255 --> 38:24.257
IT'S GET‐EVEN TIME.

38:25.692 --> 38:28.194
CAN'T WAIT
UNTIL YOUR MOTHER FINDS OUT.

38:28.194 --> 38:30.363
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WYATT.
PLEASE DON'T.

38:30.363 --> 38:34.000
YOU ARE PATHETIC,
JEFFREY.

38:34.000 --> 38:35.435
WYATT, THIS IS SO WRONG.

38:35.435 --> 38:37.337
GIVE ME YOUR KEYS.

38:37.337 --> 38:38.705
WYATT,
I'M NOT GIVING YOU MY KEYS.

38:38.705 --> 38:40.340
GIVE ME YOUR KEYS.
WHERE ARE YOU GONNA GO?

38:40.340 --> 38:42.208
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
WYATT, PLEASE DON'T DO THIS.

38:42.208 --> 38:43.744
GIVE ME YOUR DAMN KEYS.
PLEASE DON'T DO THIS.

38:43.744 --> 38:45.078
NO, NO, NO. I'M NOT ‐‐

38:45.078 --> 38:46.780
[ GRUNTS ]

38:46.780 --> 38:48.949
WHERE ARE THEY?

38:48.949 --> 38:49.850
GIVE THEM TO ME.

38:49.850 --> 38:51.317
GET AWAY FROM ME, WYATT.

38:51.317 --> 38:52.653
NO, I'M NOT LETTING YOU ‐‐

38:52.653 --> 38:54.020
GIVE ME YOUR KEYS
RIGHT NOW.

38:54.020 --> 38:56.256
WYATT, PLEASE, NO.
I LOVE YOU. PLEASE JUST ‐‐

38:56.256 --> 38:58.491
OKAY, FINE. I'M GONNA
CALL YOUR MOM RIGHT NOW.

38:58.491 --> 39:00.093
NO.
WHERE ARE YOU GONNA GO?

39:00.093 --> 39:01.134
WHERE ARE YOU GONNA GO?

39:01.134 --> 39:02.703
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
COME ON. DON'T.

39:02.703 --> 39:04.237
WYATT. PLEASE.
GIVE ME THE DAMN KEYS.

39:04.237 --> 39:05.739
NO, I'M NOT GIVING YOU ‐‐

39:05.739 --> 39:07.207
JUST TELL ME ‐‐

39:07.207 --> 39:08.308
WYATT, DON'T.

39:08.308 --> 39:10.977
WYATT.
YOU'RE NOT GOING ‐‐

39:12.312 --> 39:14.380
WAIT. WAIT.

39:14.380 --> 39:15.682
WYATT. OKAY.

39:31.698 --> 39:32.833
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

39:32.833 --> 39:34.568
COME IN.

39:46.112 --> 39:48.148
THANK YOU.

39:48.148 --> 39:50.450
YOU'RE WELCOME.

39:52.118 --> 39:54.254
FOR WHAT?

39:54.254 --> 39:56.356
HELPING MY BROTHER.

39:56.356 --> 39:57.691
OH.

39:57.691 --> 39:59.760
I DIDN'T HAVE ANYTHING
TO DO WITH THAT.

39:59.760 --> 40:02.368
WELL,
HE'S FREE FOR SOME REASON,

40:02.368 --> 40:05.205
AND I...
I THOUGHT YOU DID.

40:05.205 --> 40:08.842
GLAD HE'S OUT,
BUT IT WASN'T ME.

40:10.811 --> 40:12.412
OKAY.

40:13.614 --> 40:17.483
LISTEN, I'M SO SORRY
FOR ALL OF THIS.

40:19.119 --> 40:24.324
I'M GONNA HONOR YOUR WISHES
AND NEVER BOTHER YOU AGAIN.

40:27.027 --> 40:28.261
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

40:28.261 --> 40:30.797
CANDACE, ARE YOU SURE

40:30.797 --> 40:33.499
THAT THAT WOULD BE
HONORING MY WISHES?

40:33.499 --> 40:35.335
WELL, IT DOESN'T MATTER NOW

40:35.335 --> 40:37.971
BECAUSE ‐‐
BECAUSE THEY'RE MY WISHES.

40:37.971 --> 40:39.405
MM.

40:42.543 --> 40:47.347
I MISSED YOU.

40:47.347 --> 40:48.348
JIM.

40:48.348 --> 40:49.750
I DID.

40:49.750 --> 40:51.518
[ SIGHS ]

40:51.518 --> 40:54.655
THERE ARE A LOT OF GIRLS
YOU CAN CALL.

40:54.655 --> 40:56.690
YEAH.
A LOT OF GIRLS I CAN CALL,

40:56.690 --> 40:59.425
BUT NOT ONE OF THEM ‐‐
NOT ONE ‐‐ IS LIKE YOU.

40:59.425 --> 41:02.168
NOT ONE.

41:02.168 --> 41:04.638
SO, WHY DON'T YOU
LOCK THE DOOR?

41:04.638 --> 41:05.839
NO.

41:05.839 --> 41:07.040
NO?

41:07.040 --> 41:08.575
NO.

41:10.811 --> 41:14.314
NO, THIS HAS GOTTEN TOO
COMPLICATED AND TOO TENSE.

41:14.314 --> 41:15.549
TOO COMPLICATED?

41:15.549 --> 41:16.517
YES.
NO, NO.

41:16.517 --> 41:17.784
IT'S NOT COMPLICATED.
STOP IT.

41:17.784 --> 41:18.685
IT'S FUN.

41:18.685 --> 41:20.521
JIM.

41:20.521 --> 41:21.688
YOU KNOW YOU WANT TO.

41:21.688 --> 41:23.123
YOU DO.
STOP IT.

41:23.123 --> 41:24.591
STOP.

41:24.591 --> 41:25.792
[ DOOR OPENS ]
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, STOP?

41:25.792 --> 41:26.827
Candace: JIM ‐‐

41:26.827 --> 41:28.494
I DON'T WANT TO
STOP YOU.

41:28.494 --> 41:30.096
WHAT?
NO.

41:37.203 --> 41:39.472
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:39.472 --> 41:42.342
DARLING, YOU CAN'T GET AHEAD
BY GIVING IT.

41:42.342 --> 41:43.977
YOU WANT TO BET?

41:43.977 --> 41:45.846
AS LONG AS YOU'RE BY MY SIDE,
I'LL TELL MY MOTHER.

41:45.846 --> 41:46.847
DOESN'T MATTER, WYATT.

41:46.847 --> 41:47.981
I'M NOT GAY!

41:47.981 --> 41:50.083
SO, THERE'S NO MONEY.
WE'RE DONE?

41:50.083 --> 41:52.753
YOU ARE FREE AND CLEAR.

41:52.753 --> 41:53.854
I KNOW.

41:56.322 --> 41:58.191
WYATT.
I DIDN'T SEE HIM.

41:58.191 --> 41:59.993
KILLED WHO?
I THINK I KILLED HIM.

41:59.993 --> 42:01.735
KILLED WHO?
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

42:01.735 --> 42:05.438
MOM, DAD...

42:05.438 --> 42:07.473
I NEED TO
TELL YOU SOMETHING.
